import React from 'react';
import './style.scss';

export default function UnderConstructionAnimation() {

    return (
        <>
            .loader
            .loader_overlay
            .loader_cogs
            .loader_cogs__top
            -(1..3).each do
            .top_part
            .top_hole
            .loader_cogs__left
            -(1..3).each do
            .left_part
            .left_hole
            .loader_cogs__bottom
            -(1..3).each do
            .bottom_part
            .bottom_hole
        </>
    )
}
